      "source": [
        "# Autoimmune Diagnosis — ML Pipeline\n",
        "\n",
        "**Goal:** Clean data → pick **simple features** → compare models → cross-validate → tune XGBoost → report results.  \n",
        "**Design:** Small, understandable feature set (basic labs, vitals, demographics). No overfitting. Clear metrics.\n",
        "\n",
        "**What we do**\n",
        "1) Preprocess (impute, scale)  \n",
        "2) **Select SIMPLE features** (few labs/vitals/demographics, low-cardinality categories)  \n",
        "3) Compare models (pick XGBoost)  \n",
        "4) Cross-validation (10-Fold, LOO, LOGO, Repeated KFold)  \n",
        "5) Mild GridSearchCV (generalizable, not “too perfect”)  \n",
        "6) ROC, confusion matrix, optional regression  \n",
        "7) Methods & Results\n"
      ]
    },
